  <p><lb n="1"/>1 he dhīrāḥ sa bhagavān_ sevyatāṃ · dhairyaśālina eva sevituṃ śaknuvaṃti iti tān eva saṃbodhayati | sa kaḥ yasya guṇāḥ maitrīmaryādayo 'ṇimādayo vā · anaghāḥ niṣpāpāḥ rāgādyasaṃvalitā iti yāvat | <lb n="2"/>yasya kiṃbhūtasya · jñānadayā sindhoḥ jñānaṃ samastaviṣayā'vabodhaḥ svārtham anapekṣa paraduḥkhaharaṇecchā dayā · tayor ambutulyāyāḥ sindhor iva sindhoḥ | sindhuśabdo 'tra vipulādhāratvād upacaritaḥ sindhusā<lb n="3"/>myam · agādhasya anavacchinnamahimna <space/> sa kiṃbhūtaḥ akṣayaḥ maraṇādirahitaḥ kasmai prayojanāyai · śriye · lakṣmīsarasvatīdhītrivargasaṃpadvibhūtaye | punaḥ kasmai prayojanāya · amṛtāya mokṣāya || 1 ||</p>
